{"snp4.16:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.16 ","snp4.16:0.2":"Sariputtasutta ","snp4.16:1.1":"“Na me dittho ito pubbe, ","snp4.16:1.2":"(iccayasma sariputto) ","snp4.16:1.3":"Na suto uda kassaci; ","snp4.16:1.4":"Evam vagguvado sattha, ","snp4.16:1.5":"Tusita ganimagato. ","snp4.16:2.1":"Sadevakassa lokassa, ","snp4.16:2.2":"yatha dissati cakkhuma; ","snp4.16:2.3":"Sabbam tamam vinodetva, ","snp4.16:2.4":"ekova ratimajjhaga. ","snp4.16:3.1":"Tam buddham asitam tadim, ","snp4.16:3.2":"akuham ganimagatam; ","snp4.16:3.3":"Bahunamidha baddhanam, ","snp4.16:3.4":"atthi panhena agamam. ","snp4.16:4.1":"Bhikkhuno vijigucchato, ","snp4.16:4.2":"bhajato rittamasanam; ","snp4.16:4.3":"Rukkhamulam susanam va, ","snp4.16:4.4":"pabbatanam guhasu va. ","snp4.16:5.1":"Uccavacesu sayanesu, ","snp4.16:5.2":"kivanto tattha bherava; ","snp4.16:5.3":"Yehi bhikkhu na vedheyya, ","snp4.16:5.4":"nigghose sayanasane. ","snp4.16:6.1":"Kati parissaya loke, ","snp4.16:6.2":"gacchato agatam disam; ","snp4.16:6.3":"Ye bhikkhu abhisambhave, ","snp4.16:6.4":"pantamhi sayanasane. ","snp4.16:7.1":"Kyassa byappathayo assu, ","snp4.16:7.2":"kyassassu idha gocara; ","snp4.16:7.3":"Kani silabbatanassu, ","snp4.16:7.4":"pahitattassa bhikkhuno. ","snp4.16:8.1":"Kam so sikkham samadaya, ","snp4.16:8.2":"ekodi nipako sato; ","snp4.16:8.3":"Kammaro rajatasseva, ","snp4.16:8.4":"niddhame malamattano”. ","snp4.16:9.1":"“Vijigucchamanassa yadidam phasu, ","snp4.16:9.2":"(sariputtati bhagava) ","snp4.16:9.3":"Rittasanam sayanam sevato ce; ","snp4.16:9.4":"Sambodhikamassa yathanudhammam, ","snp4.16:9.5":"Tam te pavakkhami yatha pajanam. ","snp4.16:10.1":"Pancannam dhiro bhayanam na bhaye, ","snp4.16:10.2":"Bhikkhu sato sapariyantacari; ","snp4.16:10.3":"Damsadhipatanam sarisapanam, ","snp4.16:10.4":"Manussaphassanam catuppadanam. ","snp4.16:11.1":"Paradhammikanampi na santaseyya, ","snp4.16:11.2":"Disvapi tesam bahubheravani; ","snp4.16:11.3":"Athaparani abhisambhaveyya, ","snp4.16:11.4":"Parissayani kusalanuesi. ","snp4.16:12.1":"Atankaphassena khudaya phuttho, ","snp4.16:12.2":"Sitam athunham adhivasayeyya; ","snp4.16:12.3":"So tehi phuttho bahudha anoko, ","snp4.16:12.4":"Viriyam parakkammadalham kareyya. ","snp4.16:13.1":"Theyyam na kare na musa bhaneyya, ","snp4.16:13.2":"Mettaya phasse tasathavarani; ","snp4.16:13.3":"Yadavilattam manaso vijanna, ","snp4.16:13.4":"Kanhassa pakkhoti vinodayeyya. ","snp4.16:14.1":"Kodhatimanassa vasam na gacche, ","snp4.16:14.2":"Mulampi tesam palikhanna titthe; ","snp4.16:14.3":"Athappiyam va pana appiyam va, ","snp4.16:14.4":"Addha bhavanto abhisambhaveyya. ","snp4.16:15.1":"Pannam purakkhatva kalyanapiti, ","snp4.16:15.2":"Vikkhambhaye tani parissayani; ","snp4.16:15.3":"Aratim sahetha sayanamhi pante, ","snp4.16:15.4":"Caturo sahetha paridevadhamme. ","snp4.16:16.1":"Kimsu asissami kuva va asissam, ","snp4.16:16.2":"Dukkham vata settha kvajja sessam; ","snp4.16:16.3":"Ete vitakke paridevaneyye, ","snp4.16:16.4":"Vinayetha sekho aniketacari. ","snp4.16:17.1":"Annanca laddha vasananca kale, ","snp4.16:17.2":"Mattam so janna idha tosanattham; ","snp4.16:17.3":"So tesu gutto yatacari game, ","snp4.16:17.4":"Rusitopi vacam pharusam na vajja. ","snp4.16:18.1":"Okkhittacakkhu na ca padalolo, ","snp4.16:18.2":"Jhananuyutto bahujagarassa; ","snp4.16:18.3":"Upekkhamarabbha samahitatto, ","snp4.16:18.4":"Takkasayam kukkucciyupachinde. ","snp4.16:19.1":"Cudito vacibhi satimabhinande, ","snp4.16:19.2":"Sabrahmacarisu khilam pabhinde; ","snp4.16:19.3":"Vacam pamunce kusalam nativelam, ","snp4.16:19.4":"Janavadadhammaya na cetayeyya. ","snp4.16:20.1":"Athaparam panca rajani loke, ","snp4.16:20.2":"Yesam satima vinayaya sikkhe; ","snp4.16:20.3":"Rupesu saddesu atho rasesu, ","snp4.16:20.4":"Gandhesu phassesu sahetha ragam. ","snp4.16:21.1":"Etesu dhammesu vineyya chandam, ","snp4.16:21.2":"Bhikkhu satima suvimuttacitto; ","snp4.16:21.3":"Kalena so samma dhammam parivimamsamano, ","snp4.16:21.4":"Ekodibhuto vihane tamam so”ti. ","snp4.16:21.5":"Sariputtasuttam solasamam. ","snp4.16:21.6":"Atthakavaggo catuttho. ","snp4.16:22.0":"Tassuddanam ","snp4.16:22.1":"Kamam guhanca duttha ca, ","snp4.16:22.2":"suddhanca parama jara; ","snp4.16:22.3":"Metteyyo ca pasuro ca, ","snp4.16:22.4":"magandi purabhedanam. ","snp4.16:23.1":"Kalaham dve ca byuhani, ","snp4.16:23.2":"punadeva tuvattakam; ","snp4.16:23.3":"Attadandavaram suttam, ","snp4.16:23.4":"theraputthena solasa; ","snp4.16:23.5":"Iti etani suttani, ","snp4.16:23.6":"sabbanatthakavaggikati. "}